@ApiService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5472

### Create Order
POST {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "8fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 99.99,
      "currency": "USD"
    }
  ]
}

### Get Order (replace {orderId} with actual GUID from create response)
@orderId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}
Accept: application/json

### Confirm Order
POST {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

